{
  "stem": "13079.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now I-- I hadn't made any effort to try to collect that type of information here or present it here because those people who survived, who were actually there, are far better witnesses of what went on than I would be.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Mine was second hand.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I didn't put anybody on the stand as a witness that I didn't feel was telling the truth at the time, and telling the truth because it was corroborated.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, of course.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That happened also.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] Come to mind-- absolutely.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It comes to mind I had an accused that I was trying by the name of [?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Dietsch ?] in Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was an assistant to Major Ding-Schuler who was carrying on experiments in Buchenwald like the doctors down in Dachau.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm getting so old I can hardly remember the names of all these people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But [INAUDIBLE] for example, down in Dachau.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Dr.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Well, I'm just recalling the names of doctors that come to mind at this time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "These people, they testified as to what went on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they had no reason to lie about it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Some of them were SS.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But to them they thought that what they were doing was right.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They had been so indoctrinated with the beliefs that were prevalent at that time in Nazi Germany that they were doing a service to their country.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And to them what they did was not a criminal offense at all.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But in spite of that, some of it was so absolutely inhuman that I don't care whether it was Nazis or who.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It had to be wrong for anybody who had a modicum of morality-- the barest of the essentials of morality.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "None.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
